title: Windows 8 Tips Tricks & Apps Volume 2 - 2013  UK
description:
Windows 8 Tips, Tricks & Apps Volume 2 - 2013  UK

180 Pages | True PDF | English | 29 MB 


An all-in-one guide to get the most from Windows 8. With the latest version of Windows being the most dramatic since the introduction of the Start Button, this book covers all you need to know about the new interface and how it works in conjunction with the desktop to bring you the best computing experience. Full of helpful tips and tricks to further your knowledge of your PC, this is the perfect book for any Windows 8 and 8.1 user.
